==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gittith
<hw>Git"tith</hw> <pr>(g⟦icr⟧t"t⟦icr⟧th)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Heb.]</ety> <def>A musical instrument, of unknown character,
supposed by some to have been used by the people of Gath, and thence
obtained by David. It is mentioned in the title of Psalms viii., lxxxi.,
and lxxxiv.</def> <rj><au>Dr. W. Smith.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Giust</ent>⟦br⟧
